'''热带风暴奥尔加'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Olga}}）是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]第15场获得命名的风暴，系统源于[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]最北部以东的低气压区，形成时飓风季已经正式结束超过1星期。低气压缓慢获得热带天气系统特征，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于12月10日晚将位于[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以北近海的天气系统归类成亚热带风暴奥尔加，并且很快就成为[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]的[[热带风暴泽塔|热带风暴泽塔]]后首场在飓风季正式结束后形成的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，2007年大西洋飓风季也由此成为历史上第4个在正式时间段[[2007年亚热带风暴安德烈亚|之前]]和之后都有风暴形成的飓风季。12月11日，奥尔加从[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]最东端登陆，并在不久后转变成热带风暴。气旋经[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，然后在强烈[[风切变|风切变]]和干燥空气的不利影响下于12月13日清晨退化成残留低气压。

奥尔加影响的许多地区在1个月前还曾经受过[[飓风诺埃尔|热带风暴诺埃尔]]的摧残。波多黎各降下中等程度雨量，造成1人死亡。多米尼加共和国确认有37人丧生，其中单[[圣地亚哥省_(多米尼加)|圣地亚哥省]]的水坝泄洪就导致35人遇难。[[海地|海地]]也有两人死亡，将风暴导致的遇难人数提升到40。奥尔加不但是有纪录以来为数不多的几场在飓风季结束后登陆的大西洋热带气旋之一，也是造成人员丧生最多的一场。<ref>{{cite report | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | year = 2007 | title = Situation Reports: Caribbean: Tropical storm Olga – Dec 2007, Dominican Republic: Tropical storm Olga OCHA Situation Report No. 3 | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2013-10-18 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131018075124/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/B4901CA7C4AA9EFD492573B8001F544B-Full_Report.pdf | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/B4901CA7C4AA9EFD492573B8001F544B-Full_Report.pdf | date =  }}</ref>

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Olga 2007 track.png}}
12月上旬，一片向西移动的上层低气压在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]北部以东较远处海域发展出广阔的下层[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="report">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/ms-word/TCR-AL172007_Olga.doc | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104120657/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/ms-word/TCR-AL172007_Olga.doc | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Olga | date = 2008-01-24 | author = Michelle Mainelli | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2012-11-04 | format = DOC | publisher = National Hurricane Center }}</ref><ref name="rain">{{cite web | first = David | last = Roth | year = 2007 | title = Rainfall Summary for Tropical Storm Olga | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/olga2007.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150216155539/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/olga2007.html | archivedate = 2015-02-16 | accessdate = 2015-09-19 }}</ref><ref name="twd127" />。受东北方向的强烈[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，低压槽缓慢向西移动，产生零散的[[对流|对流]]和部分气旋式转向气流<ref name="twd127">{{cite report | author = Gladys Rubio | year = 2007 | title = December 7 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]]}}</ref>。12月8日，开始有持续性的对流同低压槽和上层低气压关联起来<ref>{{cite report | author = Patricia Wallace | year = 2007 | title = December 8 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。12月9日清晨，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始采用[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]对系统进行分析<ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Tichacek | year = 2007 | title = December 9 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，多个[[热带气旋预测模型|热带气旋预测模型]]预计系统会发展出热带天气系统特征<ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Formosa | year = 2007 | title = December 9 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。系统继续向西移动，其中存在锐利的低压槽，北部还有风速达到[[烈风|烈风]]强度的区域，行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]较为温暖<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | year = 2007 | title = December 9 Special Tropical Disturbance Statement | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。12月10日，系统发展出下层环流，但对流杂乱无章而且远离中心<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | year = 2007 | title = December 10 Special Tropical Disturbance Statement | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。受南向[[风切变|风切变]]影响，系统组织并不对称<ref name="1210twd">{{cite report | author = John Cangialosi | year = 2007 | title = December 10 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。中心附近有对流稳步增长，上层低气压的位置在系统中心以南不远处，美国国家飓风中心因此于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]12月11日凌晨3点把位于[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]以东约85公里洋面的天气系统归类为亚热带风暴并以“奥尔加”（{{lang|en|Olga}}）命名<ref name="disc1">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140810210457/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref><ref name="report" />。

[[File:Olga_2007_Florida_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

成为[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]后，奥尔加的位置在大西洋西部上空强烈高压脊的东南部，气旋内部保持有层次分明的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]并向[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向移动<ref name="disc1" />。风暴在沿[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]北海岸平行移动期间略有增强<ref name="disc2">{{cite web | author = Knabb & Mainelli | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.002.shtml? | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195631/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.002.shtml }}</ref>，中心附近的对流也有增长，于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}12月11日下午18点从[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]][[蓬塔卡纳|蓬塔卡纳]]（{{lang|en|Punta Cana}}）附近登陆<ref name="disc4">{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195726/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.004.shtml? }}</ref>。飞入风暴的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]测得更紧密的风速梯度，最高风速为每小时95公里，美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|UTC}}12月12日凌晨0点将仍位于内陆上空的奥尔加重新归类为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="pa4a">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Olga Public Advisory Four-A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public_a.004.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195949/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public_a.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-20 }}</ref>。对流在风暴途经[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]中部期间急剧减弱，到达[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]时对流已经不足以保持热带气旋状态，东北方向较远处的[[雨带|雨带]]内还保有较强风力，但中心已因干燥空气和强劲风切变的不利影响变得混乱<ref name="disc7">{{cite web | author = Franklin & Mainelli | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Olga Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195740/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.007.shtml? }}</ref>。12月12日晚，中心上空的对流略有增长，但气旋这时已降级成热带低气压<ref name="disc8">{{cite web | author = Franklin & Mainelli | year = 2007 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Storm Olga Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105002305/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2012-11-05 }}</ref>。由于系统内无法持续保有显著对流，美国国家飓风中心于12月13日清晨针对位于[[京斯敦|京斯敦]]西北方向约130公里洋面的低气压发布最后一份公告<ref name="disc9">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Olga Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195954/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.009.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="report" />。

奥尔加的残留继续向西北偏西方向移动，其中仍然有明显的下层环流，在[[古巴|古巴]]和[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]附近产生零散[[雷暴|雷暴]]，其湿气还向北沿伸到[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]南部上空<ref>{{cite report | author = Gladys Rubio | year = 2007 | title = December 13 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。系统中心以东发展出小簇深层对流，其下层环流在逼近[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]海岸线期间一直层次分明<ref>{{cite report | author = Gladys Rubio | year = 2007 | title = December 14 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。由于有[[冷锋|冷锋]]从西北方向逼近中心，风暴残留转向北上进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Tichacek | year = 2007 | title = December 15 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。12月16日晚到12月17日清晨，残留低气压在逼近佛罗里达州西海岸期间增强，[[皮尼拉斯县|皮尼拉斯县]][[克利尔沃特比奇|克利尔沃特比奇]]（{{lang|en|Clearwater Beach}}）测得的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]达到热带风暴标准，阵风时速更达飓风强度。低气压最终在穿越[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]期间被逼近的冷锋吸收<ref name="rain" /><ref name="report" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
12月10日，美国国家飓风中心针对奥尔加的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]前身向小安的列斯群岛北部、波多黎各和多明尼加共和国水域发布烈风警告<ref name="1210twd" />。奥尔加归类为亚热带气旋后，多米尼加共和国政府向该国英甲诺海角（{{lang|en|Cabo Engaño}}）到[[海地|海地]]边境之间的北部海岸沿线发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，还向到[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]附近的南部海岸沿线发布了热带风暴观察预警<ref>{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Public Advisory One | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020200000/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋风力主要集中在中心以北较远的区域，因此气象机构没有向波多黎各发布热带风暴警告<ref name="disc1" />。海地政府在奥尔加登岸前不久向该国北部沿海地区发布热带风暴警告<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin & Brown | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020200004/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.003.shtml | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Public Advisory Three | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.003.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>，之后[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]，以及[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部都接获热带风暴警告<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin & Brown | year = 2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020200009/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.004.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al17/al172007.public.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga Public Advisory Four }}</ref><ref name="report" />。

[[美国国家气象局|美国气象局]]驻圣胡安办事处向包括[[库莱布拉岛|库莱布拉岛]]和[[别克斯岛|别克斯岛]]在内的整个波多黎各发布洪灾预警，岛上部分地区因预计会有长时间的暴雨而收到山洪爆发警告<ref name="prnws">{{cite web |author=Puerto Rico National Weather Service |year=2007 |title=Watches, Warnings, and Advisories for Tropical Storm Olga in Puerto Rico |accessdate=2007-12-12 |url=http://forecast.weather.gov/wwamap/wwatxtget.php?cwa=sju&wwa=all |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5U1Ss8vdV?url=http://forecast.weather.gov/wwamap/wwatxtget.php?cwa=sju |archivedate=2007-12-12 }}</ref>。[[法哈多|法哈多]]到库莱布拉岛和别克斯岛的轮渡服务在风暴来袭期间暂停<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | date = 2007-12-11 | title = Domestic News by State/Province}}</ref>。多明尼加共和国政府在15个省开设避难所，建议生活在低洼地区的居民风暴期间不要留在家中<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Melia | date = 2007-12-11 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga spreads heavy rains across Puerto Rico | publisher = Associated Press}}</ref>，共有22个社区的居民撤离<ref name="ap1211">{{cite news | author = Ramon Almanzar | date = 2007-12-11 | title = Subtropical Storm Olga forces evacuations in Dominican Republic | publisher = Associated Press}}</ref><ref name="report" />。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Olga_2007_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
波多黎各普降小到中雨，降雨量最高的是[[庞塞|庞塞]]附近，达到283毫米<ref name="rain" />。降水令岛上多条河流水位上涨，据报阿雷西博大河的水位比洪水水位还要高数英尺<ref name="prnws" />。风暴令岛上7万9000人家中停电，14万4000人失去供水<ref name="ap1211" />。波多黎各北部因降水引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，导致一辆汽车被埋，司机遇难<ref>{{cite news | author = Ramon Almanzar | date = 2007-12-12 | title = ''Tropical Storm Olga forces evacuations in Dominican Republic; one killed in Puerto Rico'' | publisher = Associated Press | archivedate = 2007-12-22 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.pr-inside.com/tropical-storm-olga-forces-evacuations-in-r344416.htm | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222132941/http://www.pr-inside.com/tropical-storm-olga-forces-evacuations-in-r344416.htm }}</ref>。

多米尼加共和国普降暴雨，局部地区雨量总计超过250毫米<ref name="pa4a" />。降水导致北亚克河沿线出现洪灾，一度对河上大坝构成威胁，如果大坝决堤，洪水可能会导致[[圣地亚哥省_(多米尼加)|圣地牙哥省]]成千上万的居民丧生。对此当地官员决定于{{lang|en|UTC}}12月12日凌晨4点打开全部6个水闸泄洪，每秒释放的水量达610万升。洪水产生的波浪高达20米，并且这时正是深夜，许多人措不及防，仅有15分钟的准备时间。根据对这一泄洪决定持负面看法的目击者证实，洪水至少夺走了35条人命<ref name="afp1215">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-12-15 | title = 40 dead in Caribbean tropical storm | agency = Agence France-Press}}</ref>，7座镇上的大量民宅被淹<ref name="lat1213">{{cite news | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2007-12-13 | title = Tropical storm leaves 14 dead}}</ref>。该国其他地区尚有2人丧生，风暴还令超过7500套房屋受损，3万4000余人逃离家园<ref name="ap1215">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-12-15 | title = Dominican officials say Tropical Storm Olga causes major crop losses}}</ref>。该国共计遭受的损失数额估计有15亿[[多米尼加比索|多米尼加比索]]（相当于2007年的4500万[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{Cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131010182824/http://reliefweb.int/report/dominican-republic/dominican-republic-tropical-storm-olga-ocha-situation-report-no-3 | title = Dominican Republic: Tropical Storm Olga OCHA Situation Report No. 3 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/dominican-republic/dominican-republic-tropical-storm-olga-ocha-situation-report-no-3 | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | date = 2007-12-20 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2013-10-10 }}</ref>。邻近的海地北部也有两人死亡<ref name="ap1214">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-12-18 | title = Dominican president orders probe into opening of dam during Tropical Storm Olga | author = Jonathan M. Katz | accessdate = 2015-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013060143/http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/world/20071218-1002-dominican-olga.html | url = http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/world/20071218-1002-dominican-olga.html | archivedate = 2012-10-13 | newspaper = The San Diego Union-Tribune | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。12月11日，特克斯和凯科斯群岛的一间气象站测得每小时58公里的持续风速<ref name="disc4" />。

风暴行经西加勒比海期间，其东北象限内的低压槽沿途从12月14日起降下暴雨，佛罗里达州荨麻岛的降雨量达到180毫米。逼近佛罗里达州期间，残留低气压中心附近及东北部偶尔有对流形成，低气压也因此增强。12月16日清晨4至5点，克利尔沃特比奇测得的[[气压|气压]]低至1002[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]），持续风速为每小时72公里，阵风时速则达126公里。随着冷锋逼近，低气压区变得混乱，尚未抵达[[太空海岸|太空海岸]]便已消散。<ref name="rain" />

